text:
{
  "prompt": "A black-and-white technical line drawing of a full-suspension step-through electric bicycle frame. The frame has a curved low top tube for easy mounting, with a rear suspension system featuring a linkage and air shock connected between the seat tube and rear triangle. The image clearly shows the mechanical geometry, including pivot points and the swingarm. The drawing emphasizes the design optimized for heavy riders (up to 145kg) and smooth shock absorption over bumpy urban sidewalks. The image is on a white background with black outlines only.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A realistic 3D concept line drawing of a step-through electric motorbike. The bike features a mid-drive motor mounted centrally near the crank area, a removable large battery pack housed inside a thick downtube, and a CCS1 electric vehicle charging port on the left side of the downtube. The front wheel is 26 inches with a road slick tire and front suspension fork, while the rear wheel is 20 inches with a fat tire and a rear swingarm connected to an air rear shock absorber. The frame is minimalist with a clean geometry, preserving a lightweight, urban design. The bike includes pedal mounts, a long ergonomic seat, and rear dropout compatible with motorcycle disc brakes.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A detailed 3D concept rendering of a high-performance electric bicycle with a step-through frame. The bike features a central mid-drive motor (1,000W), a removable 48V 60Ah battery integrated in the down tube, a 26-inch front wheel and 20-inch wide rear tire (CST Big Boat style), full suspension with a rear air shock and front suspension fork, ergonomic long saddle with pelvic support, and a minimalistic digital display on the handlebar. The frame is lightweight aluminum, and the overall design maintains a clean, classic aesthetic suitable for long-distance city riding. Sharp, black-and-white technical rendering with clear geometry.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
